àVariationsonAMÄ

TherearevariousmodificationswhicharemadetothebasicAM
systemforspecialisedapplications:

1)SingleSidebandmodulation
     Onesidebandandthecarrierarebothsuppressed.Thismeans
thatthebandwidthusedfortransmissionissmaller.However,the
receiverwillbemuchmoreexpensive,asthecarriermustbe
accuratelyre-inserted.

2)VestigialSidebandModulation
