frequency.

However,TDMcircuitryissimplerbecauseitisdigital,andthe
samedigitalencoder/decodermaybeusedtohandleallthe
channels.(wherasforFDM,manyoscillatorsofdifferent
frequenciesareneeded).Themainproblemwithitistheneedto
keepbothendssynchronised.


